### **Optimization Strategy**

Replace runtime hash table construction with **pre-built index loading** via mmap. The Storage & Index Guide provides three ready-made multi-value hash indexes:

1. **`supplier_s_nationkey_hash.bin`** ŌĆö SupplierŌåÆnation1 lookups
2. **`customer_c_nationkey_hash.bin`** ŌĆö CustomerŌåÆnation2 lookups
3. **`orders_o_custkey_hash.bin`** ŌĆö OrderŌåÆcustkey lookups

